        </li>
      </ul>
    </article>

    <i class="text-sm"
      >✈️ I took a month off post-grad to travel to Ireland/the United Kingdom,
      my first time out of the country!</i
    >

    <article>
      <h2 class="text-3xl">
        Software Engineer Intern @ Maverick Software / Thomson Reuters
      </h2>
      <i>March 2022 - May 2024</i>

      <ul class="list-inside list-disc">
        <li>
          Enabled teams to move off of our on-prem legacy software towards cloud
          solutions months earlier than planned by working with GitHub Actions.
          Generated documentation and worked with teams to integrate the tool
          with their pipelines.
        </li>
        <li>
          Strengthened the integrity of our API by writing an XML response
          parser to ensure our API responses adhered to a XSD spec.
        </li>
        <li>
          Worked with Java, Apache Tomcat, JUnit to test, automate, and develop
          APIs (50+ tests created, 30+ bug reports filed).
        </li>
        <li>
          Collaborated with full-time employees across many different domains
          within the organization to improve the product and communicated.
        </li>
        <li>Improved existing some individual test runtimes by 40%.</li>
      </ul>
